  "3045320": {
    "name": "赛博格：崛起",
    "steam_appid": 3045320,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏相关</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/0f2d51c9b9d92199af3d8fa17fa6253d.webp?t=1753068108\" width=600 height=19 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/38338c856f09db6920d98a5a74af0ceb.poster.avif?t=1753068108\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/38338c856f09db6920d98a5a74af0ceb.webm?t=1753068108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/38338c856f09db6920d98a5a74af0ceb.mp4?t=1753068108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款融合Roguelike精髓与高速激战的第一人称射击冒险游戏，引领你踏上英雄崛起与赛博格复兴的征途。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿梭于瞬息万变的动态世界中，每一次启程都是对未知的探索。沿途搜集稀有装备与零件，强化你的武器库，准备迎接那些突如其来的强力Boss战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/8b8b70a9e727ccfe6b498e73b8d326c2.poster.avif?t=1753068108\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/8b8b70a9e727ccfe6b498e73b8d326c2.webm?t=1753068108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/8b8b70a9e727ccfe6b498e73b8d326c2.mp4?t=1753068108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁英雄角色——每位英雄都拥有专属技能与战术风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备系统——让你的每一次搭配都成为战胜挑战的关键。从经典枪械到未来科技武器，如高能激光炮与电磁脉冲发射器，构建属于你的终极战斗配置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机关卡——无限可能。采用先进算法融合预设与随机元素，打造风格迥异、挑战重重的关卡，每一次游戏都是全新的冒险体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >极限操作——在速度与生死间起舞，展现你的极限操作。快速闪避敌人的猛烈攻势，利用地形与战术智慧，将敌人一一击溃。即便不慎跌倒，也能在基地迅速恢复，再次踏上征途。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集卡片——解锁永久升级。不仅增强你的个人实力，还能让你的每次突袭都更加深入敌后。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >优化游戏体验————享受丝滑流畅的操作手感。高响应性输入系统搭配底层性能优化，确保每一场战斗都能流畅进行，让你沉浸在极致的射击快感中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原声音乐激情澎湃，为这场未来世界的生存之战注入无限动力。高能量旋律与紧张刺激的游戏节奏完美融合，带你领略前所未有的听觉盛宴。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法功能</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/0f2d51c9b9d92199af3d8fa17fa6253d.webp?t=1753068108\" width=600 height=19 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随机宝箱：复活后刷新，或战场特殊位置刷新</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/e7f135bde12d8766b7439c8fe85be382.poster.avif?t=1753068108\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/e7f135bde12d8766b7439c8fe85be382.webm?t=1753068108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/e7f135bde12d8766b7439c8fe85be382.mp4?t=1753068108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/0f2d51c9b9d92199af3d8fa17fa6253d.webp?t=1753068108\" width=600 height=19 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >英雄解锁：战场获得卡片可以解锁或升级英雄</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/8cd1affef95dc3fc2ea51a3fc283ac72.poster.avif?t=1753068108\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/8cd1affef95dc3fc2ea51a3fc283ac72.webm?t=1753068108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/8cd1affef95dc3fc2ea51a3fc283ac72.mp4?t=1753068108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/0f2d51c9b9d92199af3d8fa17fa6253d.webp?t=1753068108\" width=600 height=19 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >难度选择：简单到地狱难度</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/9fe8ddcb3cd68171efbb0abc2576bd88.poster.avif?t=1753068108\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/9fe8ddcb3cd68171efbb0abc2576bd88.webm?t=1753068108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/9fe8ddcb3cd68171efbb0abc2576bd88.mp4?t=1753068108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/0f2d51c9b9d92199af3d8fa17fa6253d.webp?t=1753068108\" width=600 height=19 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器解锁：战场获得卡片，可以解锁或升级武器 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/1a457ec2d6da0606daba37b735c77987.poster.avif?t=1753068108\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/1a457ec2d6da0606daba37b735c77987.webm?t=1753068108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/1a457ec2d6da0606daba37b735c77987.mp4?t=1753068108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事背景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/0f2d51c9b9d92199af3d8fa17fa6253d.webp?t=1753068108\" width=600 height=19 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/c91efcd929e5a7e799ccf7a5050d413d.poster.avif?t=1753068108\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/c91efcd929e5a7e799ccf7a5050d413d.webm?t=1753068108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/c91efcd929e5a7e799ccf7a5050d413d.mp4?t=1753068108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事设定在遥远的2400年，人类在荒芜的沙漠中艰难求生，文明之火岌岌可危。直到一个少女在一个古老营地的废墟中，意外唤醒了一个沉睡的赛博格，希望之光再次照耀。他们携手踏上征程，穿越危机四伏的峡谷，寻找人类复兴的契机。然而，邪恶机器人与未知生物的阻挠，让这条道路充满了未知与挑战……现在，是时候拿起武器，与少女和她的守护者并肩作战，为了人类的未来，向黑暗发起挑战！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045320/extras/0f2d51c9b9d92199af3d8fa17fa6253d.webp?t=1753068108\" width=600 height=19 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
